Trinity Nightclub

Overview

Description: Trinity Nightclub is a uniquely original two level, multi-room space housing three separate rooms and a large private VIP room. Each room has a distinctive theme and décor with a full lounge, state of the art sound and lighting, internationally acclaimed DJ’s and two spacious dance floors.
